{"word":"G1976 - ἐπιῤῥάπτω - epirrháptō - ep-ir-hrap'-to - Sew on","sections":[{"paragraph":"<strong>மூல வார்த்தை / Original: </strong><span class=\"hebrewOrGreek\">ἐπιῤῥάπτω</span>"},{"paragraph":"<strong>எழுத்துமாற்றம் / Transliteration: </strong><span class=\"transliteration\">epirrháptō</span>"},{"paragraph":"<strong>ஒலிபெயர்ப்பு / Phonetic: </strong><span class=\"phonetic\">ep-ir-hrap'-to</span>"},{"paragraph":"<strong>சுருக்க விளக்கம் / Short Definition: </strong><span class=\"short-definition\">Sew on</span>"},{"paragraph":"<span class=\"parts-of-speech\"><strong>இலக்கண சொல்வகை / Part(s) of speech: </strong>Verb / வினைச்சொல்</span>"},{"paragraph":"வினைச்சொல் - இணை"},{"paragraph":"to sew upon, sew to"},{"paragraph":"<span class=\"original-in-english\"><strong>ஆங்கில மூலம் / Original in English: </strong>From <a href=\"#/G1909 - ἐπί - epí - ep-ee'/1909\">G1909</a> and the base of <a href=\"#/G4476 - ῥαφίς - rhaphís - hraf-ece'/4476\">G4476</a>; to <i>stitch upon</i>, that is, <i>fasten</i> with the needle: - sew on.</span>"},{"paragraph":""}]}